longBusinessSummary: DevMar Equities, Inc. engages in the real estate acquisition and development of multifamily/mixed-use and hospitality projects in urban locations with a focus in Florida. The company was formerly known as La Cortez Energy, Inc. and changed its name to DevMar Equities, Inc. in February 2019. DevMar Equities, Inc. is based in Birmingham, Michigan.
